I have about 60 favorite dashboards. I have a dash for each team (4), each direct report (10), each major department my teams work with, and then misc others (metrics, upgrade/patch monitoring, major projects, etc)

When I get to a meeting I it takes way too long to poke around trying to find the dash that I need. I'd love to add these into folder groups (Teams, Staff, Clients, etc) so I can find them more easily.

