I use an agile board with issues based on a simplified workflow. As soon as all sub-tasks of a given story get to the rightmost column (~final status), the story itself is proposed to be transitioned to that same final status.

It would be useful if the same behavior was implemented for epics. As soon as all stories get to the rightmost column of a board the epic is proposed to be transitioned, too.

This would ease the maintenance of related issues and achieve a more coherent behavior across issue types.

